  "data": {
    "title": "Rank Prompt: Track Your Brand Across 6 AI Search Engines",
    "excerpt": "Rank Prompt monitors your visibility in ChatGPT, Gemini, Claude & more. See the new features that make AI SEO tracking effortless.",
    "featured_image": {
      "$media": {
        "url": "https://tonyciencia.com/blog/rank-prompt-new-features.jpg",
        "alt": "Rank Prompt: Track Your Brand Across 6 AI Search Engines",
        "filename": "rank-prompt-new-features.jpg"
      }
    },
    "content": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "*Disclosure: This post contains affiliate links. If you sign up through them, I may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.*",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Every week, over 800 million people search using AI tools like ChatGPT, Perplexity, and Gemini. They ask questions. They get answers. And somewhere in those answers, your brand either shows up or it doesn't.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "That's the game now. Traditional Google rankings still matter, but AI-generated responses have become a massive discovery channel. If you're not tracking how these platforms mention (or ignore) your business, you're flying blind.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://join.rankprompt.com/647jfexhyqoo"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Enter Rank Prompt—a purpose-built tool that monitors your brand's presence across six major AI platforms and helps you improve it. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "See what Rank Prompt offers and start your free trial here",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Let's break down what's new, what makes it stand out, and why it deserves a spot in your SEO toolkit.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The AI Search Shift Is Already Here",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Remember when SEO meant optimizing for ten blue links? Those days aren't gone, but they've been joined by something bigger.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "When someone asks ChatGPT \"best project management software for small teams\" or Perplexity \"affordable email marketing tools,\" the AI generates a response with specific brand recommendations. If your company isn't in those responses, you've just lost a potential customer to a competitor who is.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This isn't theoretical. Reports from early 2026 show that AI-driven search referrals now account for a meaningful chunk of discovery traffic for SaaS companies, e-commerce brands, and content publishers. The brands that figure out AI visibility early will have a compounding advantage.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The challenge? You can't optimize what you can't measure. Before Rank Prompt, most marketers had no systematic way to track their presence across ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, Grok, and Google's AI Mode. Manual checking was tedious, inconsistent, and impossible to scale.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/what-is-rank-prompt"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Rank Prompt solves this with automated, continuous monitoring across all six platforms",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ". It's the missing infrastructure layer for AI-era SEO.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "New & Featured Functions",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Rank Prompt has rolled out several capabilities that make it one of the most complete AI visibility tools available right now. Here's what stands out:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Multi-Platform AI Visibility Reports",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The core feature tracks how your brand appears (or doesn't) across ChatGPT, Perplexity, Google AI Mode, Claude, Gemini, and Grok. You get a unified dashboard showing prompts where your brand was mentioned, prompts where competitors appeared instead, and trends over time.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The reporting interface is clean. You can filter by platform, compare date ranges, and drill into specific prompts to see exactly how AI models describe your brand. No guessing, no manual screenshot collection.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AI-Optimized Content Generation",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Rank Prompt doesn't just show you the problem—it helps you fix it. The built-in content generator creates articles and pages specifically structured to perform well in AI search results. This isn't generic AI content; it's optimized for citation patterns that language models favor.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Think of it this way: AI models pull from sources that are well-structured, authoritative, and clearly answer common questions. Rank Prompt's content tool produces exactly that kind of material, ready to publish on your site.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Citation Building with Outreach Tools",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Getting cited by AI models often depends on your broader web presence—mentions on authoritative sites, consistent NAP data, and high-quality backlinks. Rank Prompt includes outreach tools that help you identify citation opportunities and manage the process of securing them.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is a feature most SEO tools charge extra for (or don't offer at all). Having it integrated into your AI visibility platform means you can go from \"I see a gap\" to \"I'm filling it\" without switching between five different tools.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "SEO Audits (Lighthouse Integration)",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-rank-prompt"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The platform includes Lighthouse-based SEO audits that check your site's technical health. Fast pages, proper schema markup, mobile optimization—all the foundations that help AI models trust and cite your content. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Learn more about how Rank Prompt's full feature set works",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "WordPress & Shopify Integrations",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If your site runs on WordPress or Shopify, Rank Prompt connects directly. This means you can publish AI-optimized content, monitor changes, and track results without copy-pasting between platforms. The GA4 and Search Console integrations also pull in your traditional traffic data, giving you a complete picture of how AI visibility translates to actual visits.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Agent Mode",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This newer feature lets you set up an AI agent that continuously monitors specific topics, competitors, or prompts. Instead of manually running reports, the agent watches for changes and alerts you when something shifts. It's like having an AI visibility analyst on staff, except it costs a fraction of a salary.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Why Rank Prompt Stands Out",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Plenty of SEO tools exist. Ahrefs, Semrush, and Moz are all excellent for traditional search. But they weren't built for AI search visibility.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Rank Prompt was designed from the ground up to answer a specific question: \"How do AI models see my brand?\" That focus shows up in every feature.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l3",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/why-choose-rank-prompt"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Where traditional tools track keyword positions in Google's SERPs, Rank Prompt tracks brand mentions in AI-generated responses. Where traditional tools analyze backlinks for PageRank, Rank Prompt analyzes citations for AI trust signals. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's a deeper look at why Rank Prompt is the right choice for AI-era SEO",
            "marks": [
              "l3"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The platform also handles the full workflow: monitor → diagnose → create content → build citations → measure results. Most competitors offer pieces of this. Rank Prompt offers the entire chain.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Another practical advantage: the credit system is straightforward. One credit equals one prompt report, one article, or roughly two Lighthouse audits. No hidden tiers, no nickel-and-diming for basic features. You pick a plan, you get credits, you use them how you want.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
